PRIVACY POLICY
This Privacy Policy explains how 303 Solutions LLC  and Primitive Edge LLC (“303 Solutions,” “Primitive Edge LLC,” “we,” “us,” or “our”) collect, use, disclose, and protect information when you use our mobile application(s) (the “App”), our website at www.303solutionsllc.com, and any related services (collectively, the “Services”). By using the Services, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, do not use the Services.
1. Scope; Children
This Privacy Policy applies to information we collect through the Services. It does not apply to information collected by third parties, even when we link to or integrate with their services. The Services are intended only for adults 18 years of age and older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13, and we do not allow individuals under 18 to create accounts. 
2. Information We Collect
