We collect information you provide directly, including:
    • Account information, such as your name, email address, password (or third-party login identifiers), and any profile details you choose to provide;
    • Booking and registration information for courses, classes, or events, which may include your name, contact information, and any required eligibility or medical disclosures collected by our booking platform;
    • Payment information, which is collected and processed by the applicable mobile platform or our third-party booking platform; 
    • Communications you send to us, such as support inquiries, feedback, or survey responses; and
    • User-submitted content, such as comments, profile preferences, or any other information you choose to share through the App.
2.2 Training and Usage Information
As you use the App, we may collect information about your activity, including:
    • Course and event registrations, attendance, and history;
    • Diagnostic and crash data, including error logs and performance metrics; and
2.3 Device and Technical Information
We may automatically collect technical information, including:
    • Device identifiers, model, operating system and version, language, time zone, and mobile network information;
    • App version, installation and uninstallation events, and feature-usage events;
    • IP address and approximate (city or region) location derived from it;
    • Cookies, software development kits (SDKs), pixels, and similar technologies used by our analytics, error-reporting, and push-notification providers; and
    • Permissions you grant on your device (such as notifications, microphone, or audio output).
2.4 Information from Third Parties
We may receive information about you from third parties, including:
